<section class="booking-cta" id="book">
  <h2 class="section-title">book an appointment</h2>
  <p>Your well-being starts here. Take the first step toward serenity with Kalm Moments. Unwind, refresh, and let us create the perfect moment just for you.</p>
  <a href="/book" class="cta-btn">Book an Appointment</a>
